overview: Job seeker Na-young receives a letter of acceptance from a venture company called Rogue M, and she yells in delight. Bonus 400% and even the kind smile of the handsome CEO. A dream job where all the tasks assigned to Na-young are managing the power of the company server or making coffee. Na-young, a new employee who didn't want to miss her chance, endures the sexual harassment of the lesbian team leader Mi-ran and becomes a member of the company even leaving her lover Keun-ho, who was struggling with his girlfriend's sudden change.
title: New Female Employee
